{"tid":2424675,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Bitcoin/Cryptocurrency/價值 集中討論區 (103)","createTime":"2021-02-26T18:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T18:45:34.000Z","uid":63218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"58c7c7bc1df3d128eaccf3801d8eeb97866bf6e1","tid":2424675,"uid":63218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"TODAY WE PUMP <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceb68d30ae50083dcf8e86a341634948d39d998","tid":2424675,"uid":63218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:29:02.000Z","msg":"Q: 挖礦合約好唔好?<br />\nA: 唔好信任何挖礦合約(尤其係火燎森、Mr. ghost、幣少推嗰啲)，好大機會會蝕錢同拎唔返本，直接用交易所買幣仲好<br />\n<br />\nQ: 買幣咩平台入手好？<br />\nA: Binance 幣安, FTX, 火幣，理論上最好用市值大間既exchange 因為crypto係仲未好受到監管，出事未必有得賠，多人用同埋信譽良好交易所會有保障啲。唔好用不知名交易所例如JPEX(幣少scam黎)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1v1ghGoOKv1NwyePapqbYRSQ4L3zRn8p-0GnVNRPgvDM/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1v1ghGoOKv1NwyePapqbYRSQ4L3zRn8p-0GnVNRPgvDM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=c968120f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1v1ghGoOKv1NwyePapqbYRSQ4L3zRn8p-0GnVNRPgvDM/edit?usp=sharing</a> (Credit to 津巴)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 幣安要點入錢？<br />\nA: c2c (推薦)，多數用fps買，但轉數比人果時千其咪撚寫bitcoin等字眼。記住跟足賣家指示，否則有機會無晒d錢。其次可以credit card但要比3.5% fee。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 幣安要手續費？<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.binance.com/en/fee/trading\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.binance.com%2Fen%2Ffee%2Ftrading&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=25e9d509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.binance.com/en/fee/trading</a><br />\nQ: 啱啱入咗錢，有咩幣好買？<br />\nA: 買咩幣都好，最好自己做咗少少功課搵下咩嚟。懶搵資料嘅可以直接買XRP （不過自己搵下XRP啲新聞先啦。）<br />\n<br />\nQ: 想贏大錢，玩孖展好唔好？<br />\nA: 自己衡量風險，賭徒心態最易出事。有人約agent 睇樓，有人ifc 排緊隊。<br />\n<br />\nQ: All in altcoin (non bitcoin)，貪佢賺得快好多？<br />\nA: 入妖幣悔終身，比特以太更稱心。無錯係升得快，但跌到變0 嘅機會較大。<br />\n經典例子: BitConnect 一個禮拜跌到變0。<br />\n<br />\nQ: USDT=USD=Safe?<br />\nA: 現階段usdt都頗多醜聞，長線建議手持USDC同BUSD。<br />\n(Emma: settled? [25/2])<br />\n<br />\nQ: 香港玩crypto合唔合法?<br />\nA: 玩得crypto 其實就係唔想比政府干預，驚就去買返港股美股，啲錢上晒鏈邊個管到你?<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有咩資訊渠道可以參考下？<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.blocktempo.com/2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blocktempo.com%2F2021&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=afe8614d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.blocktempo.com/2021</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://cryptowesearch.com/category/newbie-guide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptowesearch.com%2Fcategory%2Fnewbie-guide%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=fff71a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cryptowesearch.com/category/newbie-guide/</a> (Credit to HKGo 巴打，歡迎follow佢IG page)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 入門建議？<br />\nA: 新入黎既巴打, 我真心建議買BTC/ ETH （正幣） HODL 1個月先<br />\n每日做mon po 狗, mon 實個市同呢度. 慢慢適應幣市節奏,之後先諗long short, 合約, 槓桿呢D.<br />\n因為幣市波幅太大, 你永遠唔會知聽日係咪幣災<br />\neven 係牛市, 回調30-40%係非常常見既事.心臟同財力都未必咁易承受到 （by Inner_Wave 巴打）<br />\n<br />\nQ: 買咗唔少crypto，驚交易所執笠，可以點算？<br />\nA: 擺crypto係exchange wallet意味住你將啲錢交比exchange 託管，你無full control。not your key, not you money.<br />\n而Cold wallet就係完全離線既wallet，可以減低被hack風險。Cold wallet可以係hardware wallet (safepal，Ledger Nano etc&hellip;) software wallet 就有: Trust Wallet，Metamask etc... 普遍交易所射錢去銀包係要手續費。切記，只有自己掌握private key嘅銀包先叫安全！！！！<br />\n<br />\nPS: 切記要記低cold wallet個recovery seed (通常都係12/24 個生字) ，拎紙抄低佢又好背咗佢又好，你一但洗咗機而你又唔記得個recovery seed咁你啲錢就會留係個wallet入面呢世都拎唔返出嚟<br />\n<br />\nQ: 追po成日見到有人講農場，farming，defi，係咩嚟架？<br />\nA: defi(去中心化金融 )係比較進階嘅玩法，defi裡面仲未好多人識用所以回報高都好誇張（誇張到好似scam, 雖然唔少都係)<br />\n<br />\n因為defi 呢個新興市場仲係好實驗性質，所以裡面暗藏大量風險，包括你farm 嘅幣幣價變0, dex 被hacker 攻擊（好多）令你資金損失，無常損失（新手自行search 下）等等，所以都仲係非常之高風險，不建議新手一入幣市就玩。<br />\n<br />\n而且呢類defi 平台係permissionless, 出事有損失你係會拎唔返啲錢<br />\n<br />\n建議先了解好幣市生態。若果要開始，可以先準備wallet，bnb，你目前有流動性嘅幣。詳情可以參考HKGo 巴嘅網 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cryptowesearch.com/2020/12/16/trust-wallet-pancakeswap/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptowesearch.com%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2Ftrust-wallet-pancakeswap%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=a17ad57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cryptowesearch.com/2020/12/16/trust-wallet-pancakeswap/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果要係trust wallet enable Dapp，可參考: <a href=\"https://community.trustwallet.com/t/enable-dapp-browser-on-trust-wallet-ios-version/98308?fbclid=IwAR3vJT6swJJrQCXJqcRBdXYL21qfQISJkQXHMvJ_ZI9_LSuVyoQ-uHiOOew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcommunity.trustwallet.com%2Ft%2Fenable-dapp-browser-on-trust-wallet-ios-version%2F98308%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3vJT6swJJrQCXJqcRBdXYL21qfQISJkQXHMvJ_ZI9_LSuVyoQ-uHiOOew&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B30iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=9366d762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://community.trustwallet.com/t/enable-dapp-browser-on-trust-wallet-ios-version/98308?fbclid=IwAR3vJT6swJJrQCXJqcRBdXYL21qfQISJkQXHMvJ_ZI9_LSuVyoQ-uHiOOew</a>"},{"pid":"767530e2754f9f5d3196f9a43b8d2aeaca641fef","tid":2424675,"uid":215700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cb0e82ca701c34497e339852f4c7ad63a15318","tid":2424675,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f5e199d1141d964a370cf095d6fec47e4205b2","tid":2424675,"uid":173376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"又割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce8d54cd6425e47e26c960745b91cf8af0bddbc","tid":2424675,"u